critical_negative: I think it all worked pretty well considering we were very different in age, gender, and what part of the country we live in. begin_memory_text: At the beginning, I talked about other ways of making money online and gave her information about how to do what she is doing more effectively.  I am burning out on these opportunities and want to share them.

end_memory_text: I mentioned some of the issues that are going on with our pet bird and how this is upsetting at the moment, particularly as we are unsure if she is going to make it or not.  This is not good!  But my partner was nice about it.
rest_of_day_open: I am going to indulge in my own activities and hope that the bird is okay, though I am concerned that she might not make it to the surgery she has scheduled on Tuesday.  I am going to see what happens and comfort my significant other about it if things do not go well.
critical_positive: Talking about my experiences making money worked well as I have a lot of experience with some of these techniques. critical_negative: I did not want to veer too much into criticizing Biden or other democrats in general, as I feel she is just looking for relief in them winning.  I am concerned that they will be ineffective even if they manage to win the election and lead to someone worse than Trump.
